{"tid":850040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"情侶買車殺到最低價！卻拿3張八萬「麻將牌」付款　遭群毆","createTime":"2018-10-06T07:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T09:29:34.000Z","uid":110385,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a09f9a0d6d31f43dcfc1d7aafb68e817373294e9","tid":850040,"uid":110385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"大陸廣東中山一對情侶為了拍「抖音」影片，日前到汽車展示間買車，不料談了半天要了各種優惠，銷售人員要他們付款時，情侶卻拿出出來3張八萬「麻將牌」付款，讓店內銷售員全傻了，直接將兩人暴打一頓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdUdCtX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsdUdCtX.jpg&h=172e9c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n綜合陸媒報導，一名情侶日前到了到4S馬自達店內說要以現金買車，並與一名男業務詳談了大半天，逼得業務員好不容易從店經理那拿到超值優惠價格，不料銷售人員準備向情侶拿錢辦理一切手續時，情侶卻拿出「3張八萬的麻將牌」說要付24萬元人民幣（約107萬元新台幣）的車款，並說「正在拍抖音」讓銷售員傻眼，直接暴打該情侶，甚至店內其他銷售員得知，也跟著追打該情侶。<br />\n<br />\n影片中可見，該情侶至少遭到7名男業務圍毆，期間女子遭推擠、摔到了地上，男子則遭緊緊抓住，遭拳頭毆打、腳踢；直到2名男子勸阻，所以人才停下動作。對此，網友看到影片後，紛紛表示「好療癒啊」、「再抖啊！欠打」、「讓人忙大班天！最後撲空該死」。<br />\n<br />\n片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=61&amp;v=JQJyuruNsPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D61%26v%3DJQJyuruNsPQ&d=tmnNc1%2F5Cp15QOcWwSiJj8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a987676e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=61&amp;v=JQJyuruNsPQ</a><br />\n<br />\n來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=438763\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D438763&d=tmnNc1%2F5Cp15QOcWwSiJj8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=d3508af2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D438763&h=cbf15296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=438763</a><br />\n<br />\n玩抖音嘅朋友可以試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80c8ec0c81b38ef8297795578f12e5f27fe9e62","tid":850040,"uid":37933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:05:59.000Z","msg":"抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cb29a8520b2d2dccc180c6026c990a7c2c01142","tid":850040,"uid":57513,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"垃圾人玩垃圾app<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367d37ee630b2804b2c9ba2ba9f4c16a40169ee2","tid":850040,"uid":69886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:09:00.000Z","msg":"龍心幾時比人打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5ee5da24da706ade3f8f39d5b74b514e37ede5","tid":850040,"uid":18477,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:09:02.000Z","msg":"3隻8萬最多攞嚟碰<br />\n點畀錢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8dce49ca3f2e56b2ec4246413115a2dd4f27856","tid":850040,"uid":65128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:09:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d90844fb75cbef6095b63865461574470b2e87f","tid":850040,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:10:39.000Z","msg":"成功上位啦<br />\n條片實大把人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecad69d686cc8668aa2a97f8decf58d0349d3149","tid":850040,"uid":96182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:11:10.000Z","msg":"一定夠哂多人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 達成目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166104a4c1339f6d789b798b13aba0a061d72063","tid":850040,"uid":132